high_descs: Take one step to the right.
Pick up the spoon off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink and wash it.
Turn right, then right again towards the microwave.
Set the spoon on the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Was the spoon and put it next to the microwave.

high_descs: Walk slightly to the right and stand in front of the spoon on the counter.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to the side table containing the microwave.
Put the spoon on the table, in front of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon on a side table.

high_descs: Take the spoon from the counter to the right
Put the spoon in the sink
Turn on the water to wash the spoon
Take the spoon out of the sink, turn around
Put the spoon on the table in front of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Wash a spoon and put it next to the microwave
